Stark öppning på Stockholmsbörsen – Powercell backar
Storbolagen stärktes rejält i den inledande måndagshandeln med SSAB i topp. Småspararfavoriten Powercell backar med 5,5 procent efter säljråd i Dagens industri.
04 Nov 2019, 08:37 by Robert Triches

Strong opening on the Stockholm Stock Exchange - Powercell backs
The major companies were significantly strengthened in the initial Monday trading with SSAB at the top. Small saver favorite Powercell backs 5.5 percent after sales advice in Today's industry.
04 Nov 2019, 08:37 by Robert Triches
